        "rendered": "More block"
    },
    "content": {
        "rendered": "\n<p class=\"has-text-align-right has-small-font-size\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/blocks/\">Go to the List of Blocks</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>The&nbsp;<em>More block</em> is used to display a &#8216;Read More&#8217; link to the full blog post, on the blog home page, or on the archive pages. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>If your theme is set to show the post\u2019s full content on archive pages or the blog home page, then a post using the <em>More block</em> truncates your blog entries so that only the part of the&nbsp;post before the <em>More block</em> is displayed on the home page and archive pages, followed by a \u201cRead More\u201d link. Clicking on the &#8216;Read More&#8217; link directs the reader to the full blog post. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>If your theme is set to show only the excerpts on the archives page and the blog home page, the <em>More block</em> is ignored. The excerpt displayed is the one <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/excerpt/\">manually entered for the post</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The More block can be placed anywhere in a post. You can customize the link to say whatever you want. You can only insert one More block in each Post.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-background\" style=\"background-color:#e5f5fa\">The More Block<strong> </strong>works only for Posts, (not Pages).</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-video\"><video autoplay controls loop muted src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2019/03/more.mp4\"></video></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And this is how it will look on your site (Styles may vary depending on your theme).</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2019/03/more-block-result.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"920\" height=\"395\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2019/03/more-block-result.png\" alt=\"How More Block works on the front end\" class=\"wp-image-11285824\" srcset=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2019/03/more-block-result.png 920w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2019/03/more-block-result-300x129.png 300w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2019/03/more-block-result-768x330.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 920px) 100vw, 920px\" /></a><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">More block (result)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>To add a More block, click on the <strong>Block Inserter</strong> icon.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also type <code>/more</code> and hit enter in a new <em>paragraph block</em> to add one quickly.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2019/03/more-block-add-typing.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"796\" height=\"296\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2019/03/more-block-add-typing.png\" alt=\"Adding More Block by typing /more\" class=\"wp-image-11285819\" srcset=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2019/03/more-block-add-typing.png 796w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2019/03/more-block-add-typing-300x112.png 300w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2019/03/more-block-add-typing-768x286.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 796px) 100vw, 796px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left has-background\" style=\"background-color:#e5f5fa\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/adding-a-new-block/\">Detailed instructions on adding blocks</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Editing the Block</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you add the block, you can edit the Read More text that appears by default by clicking in the middle of the dashed lines, erasing the text, and typing anything you want. To revert back to the default text that your theme displays, remove all the text from the More block and save your Post.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter is-resized\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2019/03/more-block-edit-text.gif\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2019/03/more-block-edit-text.gif\" alt=\"Editing the More Block text\" class=\"wp-image-11285820\" width=\"381\" height=\"233\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Block Toolbar</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Each block has its own block-specific controls that allow you to manipulate the block right in the editor. The <em>More block</em> offers the following buttons on the Block toolbar:</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Transform to<br>Drag icon<br>Move handles<br>More options</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter is-resized size-large\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/06/Screen-Shot-2022-06-23-at-8.49.10-AM.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/06/Screen-Shot-2022-06-23-at-8.49.10-AM-1024x150.png\" alt=\"Block toolbar in the More block\" class=\"wp-image-15765015\" width=\"379\" height=\"56\" srcset=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/06/Screen-Shot-2022-06-23-at-8.49.10-AM-1024x150.png 1024w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/06/Screen-Shot-2022-06-23-at-8.49.10-AM-300x44.png 300w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/06/Screen-Shot-2022-06-23-at-8.49.10-AM-768x113.png 768w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/06/Screen-Shot-2022-06-23-at-8.49.10-AM.png 1350w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 379px) 100vw, 379px\" /></a><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">You can click on the block to reveal the Block Toolbar.</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Transform to</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Click on the \u201cTransform\u201d button to convert the More block into a \u201cColumns\u201d or \u201cGroup\u201d block. \u201cGroup\u201d gives you the ability to change the background color around the More block.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/06/Screen-Shot-2022-06-23-at-8.59.57-AM-1024x283.png\" alt=\"Transform option in the More block\" class=\"wp-image-15765068\" width=\"357\" height=\"99\" srcset=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/06/Screen-Shot-2022-06-23-at-8.59.57-AM-1024x283.png 1024w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/06/Screen-Shot-2022-06-23-at-8.59.57-AM-300x83.png 300w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/06/Screen-Shot-2022-06-23-at-8.59.57-AM-768x212.png 768w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/06/Screen-Shot-2022-06-23-at-8.59.57-AM.png 1296w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 357px) 100vw, 357px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Drag icon</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"328\" height=\"108\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/06/Screen-Shot-2022-06-23-at-9.00.28-AM.png\" alt=\"Drag icon in the More Block Toolbar\" class=\"wp-image-15765072\" srcset=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/06/Screen-Shot-2022-06-23-at-9.00.28-AM.png 328w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/06/Screen-Shot-2022-06-23-at-9.00.28-AM-300x99.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 328px) 100vw, 328px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>To drag and drop the block to a new location on the page template, click and hold the rectangle of dots, then drag to the new location. The blue separator line indicates where the block will be placed. Release the left mouse button when you find the new location to place the block.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Move handles</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>The up and down arrow icons can be used to shift a block up and down on the page.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/06/Screen-Shot-2022-06-23-at-10.07.27-AM.png\" alt=\"Move handles in the More block toolbar\" class=\"wp-image-15765299\" width=\"252\" height=\"87\" srcset=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/06/Screen-Shot-2022-06-23-at-10.07.27-AM.png 336w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/06/Screen-Shot-2022-06-23-at-10.07.27-AM-300x104.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 252px) 100vw, 252px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left has-background\" style=\"background-color:#e5f5fa\"><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/moving-blocks/\" target=\"_blank\">Get more information about moving a block within the editor.</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>More options</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>These controls give you the option to copy, duplicate, and edit your block as HTML.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left has-background\" style=\"background-color:#e5f5fa\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/more-options/\">Read about these and other settings.</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Block Settings</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Every block has specific options in the editor sidebar in addition to the options found in the block toolbar.&nbsp;<em>If you do not see the sidebar, simply click the &#8216;cog&#8217; icon.</em></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/06/Screen-Shot-2022-06-23-at-9.39.34-AM.png\" alt=\"Cog icon to display the Block sidebar\" class=\"wp-image-15765217\" width=\"357\" height=\"90\" srcset=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/06/Screen-Shot-2022-06-23-at-9.39.34-AM.png 492w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/06/Screen-Shot-2022-06-23-at-9.39.34-AM-300x76.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 357px) 100vw, 357px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Block Sidebar for the More block has a toggle switch to:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-extra-large-font-size\"> Hide the excerpt on a full content page</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter is-resized size-full\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/06/Screen-Shot-2022-06-23-at-9.09.16-AM-1.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/06/Screen-Shot-2022-06-23-at-9.09.16-AM-1.png\" alt=\"Block Settings for More block\" class=\"wp-image-15765129\" width=\"361\" height=\"340\" /></a><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Block Settings for More block</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>By enabling the &#8216;<em>Hide the excerpt</em>&#8216; toggle button, the content that appears before the <em>More block</em> will not display on the full post, once the user clicks on the <em>More</em> link after the excerpt. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>This option is disabled by default. This feature is helpful if you would like to display custom excerpt on the homepage and archive pages but when the user clicks to read the full post, the excerpt is hidden.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-video\"><video controls src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/06/Screen-Recording-2022-06-23-at-9.54.42-AM-1.mp4\"></video></figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group changelog has-background is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\" style=\"background-color:#e0e0e0\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-extra-large-font-size\" id=\"changelog\">Changelog<strong> </strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>2022-11-27\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Removed redundant content </li>\n\n\n\n<li>Added headings</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Aligned images for mobile view </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Updated 2022-06-23\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Added content, images, video for 6.0</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Added ALT tags for the images</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Updated 2021-02-10\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Added Note section</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Created 2019-03-07</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n",
